  "data": {
    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you study a creature to cultivate the perfect insult. Attempt a Culture check with a DC equal to 10 + your opponent&rsquo;s total Bluff skill bonus, or 15 + 1-1/2 &times; the opponent&rsquo;s CR, whichever is greater. If you succeed, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Bluff and Intimidate checks against that opponent for 1 minute. If you spend 1 Resolve Point, allies within 60 feet also gain this bonus for the same duration. Once you&rsquo;ve attempted to craft a perfect insult against a creature, you can&rsquo;t target that creature again with this ability for 24 hours.</p>",
